This is an applications to handle maillists.

To install:
  1. Install as any other python package - setup.py, pip..
  2. Add 'maillist' to INSTALLED_APPS
  3. Symlink mailist/media/maillist to MEDIA_ROOT 

Package includes simple test project, maillist_test. To run it:
  1. Symlink application media (step 3 of installation).
  2. python manage.py syncdb.
  3. python manage.py loaddata fixtures/test_data.json.
  4. python manage.py runserver
